data.description: Lovely single family home on a DOUBLE LOT! Welcome to 4139 Mountain View Ave. where the name of the street is indicative of the views surrounding this home. Nestled in the Red Bank community at the foot of Signal Mountain, one can enjoy the scenic surroundings while also enjoying the convenience to shopping, dining and schools. There are 3 spacious bedrooms, 2 1/2 bathrooms, formal dining and second den/office areas. The galley kitchen has stainless appliances and eat-in area for additional dining. Step out back to enjoy the newly renovated deck with partially open and partially covered, screened areas. To the right side of the yard, there is a large, fenced area perfect for kids, pets and entertaining. There is also an out building on site for lawn and play equipment. Many updates have been made to the home, including: Trane HVAC units installed in March of 2021 w/10-year transferable warranty, water heater was installed in 2022,  picket fence was installed in 2020, dishwasher was installed in 2022, recently remodeled: screened-in back porch, painted back porch, new flooring in office, updated entrance way for office with new awning, updated front patio/entrance, updated downstairs bathroom. Conveniently located and just a 5 minute drive to downtown. This and so much more await. Contact me for more information or for a tour!
